pickle-desc: Adde le tests basic de Pickle al modulos Lua
pickle-function-text-todo-good: $1 ha passate con cosas a facer
pickle-function-text-todo-fail: $1 ha fallite con cosas a facer
pickle-tracking-category-good-desc: Le resultato indica un stato “passate” post le evalutation del tests.
pickle-tracking-category-pending-desc: Le resultato indica un stato “pendente” post le evalutation del tests.
pickle-tracking-category-todo-desc: Le resultato indica que un o plus marcator(es) “cosas a facer” ha essite trovate post le evalutation del tests.
pickle-tracking-category-skip-desc: Le resultato indica que un o plus marcator(es) “saltate” ha essite trovate post le evalutation del tests.
pickle-tracking-category-fail-desc: Le resultato indica un stato “fallite” post le evalutation del tests.
pickle-tracking-category-missing-desc: Le resultato indica un pagina de test “mancante” post le evalutation del tests.
pickle-tracking-category-unknown-desc: Le resultato indica un stato “incognite” post le evalutation del tests.
pickle-track-log-header: Iste registro monstra un summario de resultatos de cambiamentos de modulos testate.
pickle-track-log-entry-good: {{GENDER:$2|ha inferite automaticamente}} que $1 ha passate tote le tests
pickle-track-log-entry-todo-good: {{GENDER:$2|ha inferite automaticamente}} que $1 ha passate con tests incomplete
pickle-track-log-entry-todo-fail: {{GENDER:$2|ha inferite automaticamente}} que $1 ha fallite con tests incomplete
pickle-track-log-entry-skip-good: {{GENDER:$2|ha inferite automaticamente}} que $1 ha passate con tests saltate
pickle-track-log-entry-skip-fail: {{GENDER:$2|ha inferite automaticamente}} que $1 ha fallite con tests saltate
pickle-track-log-entry-fail: {{GENDER:$2|ha inferite automaticamente}} que $1 ha fallite alcun tests
pickle-track-log-entry-exists: {{GENDER:$2|ha inferite automaticamente}} que $1 ha un pagina de test
pickle-track-log-entry-missing: {{GENDER:$2|ha inferite automaticamente}} que $1 non ha un pagina de test
pickle-track-log-entry-unknown: {{GENDER:$2|ha inferite automaticamente}} que $1 ha tests incognite
pickle-report-skip-no-message: Le clave de message “$1” non existe
pickle-adapt-process-as-upper: Mitter in majusculas tote le characteres del catena
pickle-adapt-process-as-lower: Mitter in minusculas tote le characteres del catena
pickle-adapt-process-as-upper-first: Mitter in majuscula le prime character del catena
pickle-adapt-process-as-lower-first: Mitter in minuscula le prime character del catena
pickle-adapt-process-as-u-upper: Mitter in majusculas tote le catena Unicode
pickle-adapt-process-as-u-lower: Mitter in minusculas tote le catena Unicode
pickle-adapt-process-as-u-upper-first: Mitter in majuscula le prime puncto de codice del catena Unicode
pickle-adapt-process-as-u-lower-first: Mitter in minuscula le prime puncto de codice del catena Unicode
pickle-adapt-process-as-u-n-f-c: Recodificar la catena Unicode in Forma Normalisate C (NFC)
pickle-adapt-process-as-u-n-f-d: Recodificar la catena Unicode in Forma Normalisate D (NFD)
pickle-adapt-process-as-round: Trovar le numero integre le plus proxime
pickle-adapt-process-as-integer: Trovar le parte de numero integre
pickle-adapt-condition-to-be-boolean-equ: Debe esser booleanmente equal al destination (se evaluta al mesme valor boolean)
pickle-adapt-condition-to-be-strict-equa: Debe esser strictemente equal al destination (equalitate exacte e de typo)
pickle-adapt-condition-to-be-same: Debe esser le mesme que le destination (equal post conversion de typos)
pickle-adapt-condition-to-be-deep-equal: Debe esser profundemente equal al destination (compara tabellas recursivemente)
pickle-adapt-condition-to-be-contained: Debe esser continite in le destination
pickle-adapt-condition-to-be-lesser-than: Debe esser minor que le destination
pickle-adapt-condition-to-be-greater-tha: Debe esser major que le destination
pickle-adapt-condition-to-be-lesser-or-e: Debe esser minor que o equal al destination
pickle-adapt-condition-to-be-greater-or-: Debe esser major que o equal al destination
pickle-adapt-condition-to-be-match: Le valor como texto debe apparer in le destination
pickle-adapt-condition-to-be-u-match: Le valor como texto in Unicode debe apparer in le destination
